WEBVTT

00:01.196 --> 00:03.290
Don't bombard your team with messages.

00:03.742 --> 00:05.785
Each time you email, text or call,...

00:06.052 --> 00:10.015
...imagine that you are physically walking into your colleague's workspace.

00:10.522 --> 00:13.168
If you followed up an email by text and phone,...

00:13.256 --> 00:16.795
...it would be like opening their office door three times in a row.

00:17.397 --> 00:21.963
Minimize your digital volume and think wisely before hitting "send."

